    tldr: 'EU childcare and nursery businesses operate in a regulated, labour-intensive sector with significant government funding interaction across most member states. Financial sustainability requires fee rates that cover full operational costs beyond government subsidy levels, staff cost management within 55–65% of revenue, and proactive capacity management. Many nurseries that struggle financially are inadvertently cross-subsidising government-funded places from private-fee revenue.',
